(copied from https://oatpp.io/about/)

Oat++ is an open-source C++ web framework for highly scalable and
resource-efficient web applications.
It provides all the necessary components for production-grade development,
including:

 - Advanced REST framework with request parameters mapping and
   Swagger-UI annotations
 - ORM Framework
 - WebSocket framework
 - Object Mapping
 - Dependency Injection
 - Swagger-UI

It's zero-dependency, easy-portable, and high-performance.

